				<td colspan="2"><span>Kinda like Bruscos. They have significantly more range. Equipping a drum/percussion instrument will significantly increase the damage done by chants, but not by Brusco's. They do not have any stun/knockback. They debuff resists. 
<br />

<br />
Theoretically, you could have started killing HGs at 30, althougth would be a long slow proccess. Yes, at 38 you can kill HGs fine, if not too quickly.</span></td>
