				<td colspan="2"><span>You can Chant Kite HGs at lvl 30.  It just takes a LONG time!  Goes much faster after lvl 38.
<br />

<br />
Fear Kiting there can be tough, and I do NOT recommend doing it in your early 30s.  You will get resisted too much, giving them a chance to beat on you, which they will do quite effectively when you are that low! lol
<br />

<br />
Fear Kiting, however, is very nicely adaptable to group play.  Any added DPS, either melee or otherwise, will make them die faster while you keep them feared and snared.</span></td>
